00:12:07.122 --> 00:12:07.903
SO

00:12:07.903 --> 00:12:10.012
ven s'iz gekumen

00:12:10.012 --> 00:12:12.408
di tsayt fun di milkhome

00:12:12.408 --> 00:12:16.549
vos gedenkstu? vi nokh hot zikh geendert di, geendikt dos lebn?

00:12:15.998 --> 00:12:17.629
ikh gedenk azoy.

00:12:17.652 --> 00:12:22.272
az mir zenen oyfgeshtanen iz gefloygn f- a por eroplanen

00:12:22.272 --> 00:12:24.852
un m'hot gevorfn papirlekh.

00:12:24.852 --> 00:12:27.282
iz geven d- UNK ⟨eyn mol⟩ fun papirn

00:12:27.282 --> 00:12:28.842
hob ikh gekhapt di papirn

00:12:28.842 --> 00:12:30.673
un ikh hob nisht gekent keyn rusish nokh.

00:12:30.865 --> 00:12:32.901
hot men d- mayn foter gekent.

00:12:33.227 --> 00:12:39.704
hot men ibergelezn "f- shvester un brider, mir, royter armey, zenen mir gekumen bafrayen fun, fun di

00:12:39.704 --> 00:12:40.792
fun di

00:12:40.792 --> 00:12:42.957
poylishe kapitalistn

00:12:42.964 --> 00:12:48.931
un, se kum- der royter armey vet aykh bafrayen un zayn fray. yeder vet zayn glaykh"

00:12:49.123 --> 00:12:50.309
un azoy

00:12:50.309 --> 00:12:52.719
un ⟨durkh⟩ a tog zenen zey ongekumen di rusn.

00:12:52.719 --> 00:12:55.219
iz geven, gedenk ikh di tanken

00:12:55.219 --> 00:12:58.850
un, un, s'iz geven azoyne vogns, gaz

00:12:58.850 --> 00:13:00.930
dos FORD meyn ikh iz dos geven.

00:13:00.930 --> 00:13:03.123
amerikanishe FORDn vos zey hobn f-

00:13:03.349 --> 00:13:05.489
gegebn far, far Rusland tsi vos

00:13:05.489 --> 00:13:06.329
azoyne

00:13:06.370 --> 00:13:08.861
di, di, di vogn zenen geven azoy

00:13:09.103 --> 00:13:11.527
⟨royt⟩ UNK kindershe vogn yetst

00:13:11.854 --> 00:13:16.336
un zey hobn gegebn shvebelekh, un s'iz geven ongeshribn oyf di shvebelekh

00:13:17.423 --> 00:13:20.820
far kinder azoy: S.S.S.R.

00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:22.833
ts- dray S. un R.

00:13:23.025 --> 00:13:24.465
hot men getaytsht

00:13:24.465 --> 00:13:26.321
shpeter, a por teg tsurik

00:13:26.321 --> 00:13:30.747
az UNK "s'iz nisht geven, s'vet nisht zayn, s'iz nishto, redt zikh nisht ayn."

00:13:38.027 --> 00:13:38.831
un

00:13:39.343 --> 00:13:41.412
me ken a bisl lakhn oykhet.

00:13:40.221 --> 00:13:41.514
yo.

00:13:41.655 --> 00:13:43.235
biz tsu di tsores.

00:13:44.656 --> 00:13:46.841
