00:13:46.841 --> 00:13:53.394
fun di daytshn vos hot pasirt in EUROPE un mit Hitler, hostu gekent fun di zakhn?

00:13:50.818 --> 00:13:51.875
yo.

00:13:52.573 --> 00:13:54.148
yo, ikh hob gekent.

00:13:54.148 --> 00:13:57.562
