00:13:57.855 --> 00:13:59.823
se kumt a shvere tsayt"

00:14:00.049 --> 00:14:01.376
dos iz geven

00:14:01.821 --> 00:14:03.823
nokhn nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:14:04.183 --> 00:14:05.307
meyn ikh azoy.

00:14:06.327 --> 00:14:08.194
"un me darf antloyfn.

00:14:08.453 --> 00:14:09.577
me harget yidn."

00:14:11.102 --> 00:14:15.669
