00:14:20.316 --> 00:14:22.118
s'iz UNK televizors dokh nisht geven.

00:14:22.118 --> 00:14:24.225
ven di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn

00:14:24.366 --> 00:14:27.515
mit, mit Poyln

00:14:27.673 --> 00:14:31.261
hob ikh gehert redn RYDZ SMIGLY. dos iz geven der prezident

00:14:31.723 --> 00:14:33.371
fun Poyln.

00:14:33.580 --> 00:14:37.388
in Poylish, vos ikh gedenk yetst, hot er gesh- hot er geredt

00:14:37.562 --> 00:14:39.716
az,

00:14:40.110 --> 00:14:44.916
"⟨NIE DAMY BOLSZEWICKE NODZE UNK NASZE DRODZE⟩"

00:14:44.916 --> 00:14:46.213
mir ⟨veln⟩ nisht lozn

00:14:46.219 --> 00:14:50.583
di di BOLSZEWICKI fis, es zol durkhgeyn oyf undzer veg."

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:51.376
vayl

00:14:51.450 --> 00:14:55.932
"⟨PO⟩ ANGLIA I AMERYKA ⟨IDJE⟩ NA POMOC POLSCE"

00:14:56.057 --> 00:14:59.341
ANGLIA un Amerike geyt helfn Poyln."

