iz der foter hot gezogt "⟨gib a⟩ kuk. aza land vi Amerike mit England mit ale geyen helfn, vos hobn mir moyre?"

00:15:08.545 --> 00:15:10.682
un azoy iz dos geblibn.

00:15:11.042 --> 00:15:14.850
nor di, ven di rusn zenen arayn, iz a sakh mentshn

00:15:14.873 --> 00:15:17.077
ver s'iz geven a gvir hot gehat mazl.

00:15:17.320 --> 00:15:19.102
m'hot im avekgeshikt keyn Sibir.

00:15:20.087 --> 00:15:21.903
di ale gvirim

00:15:22.112 --> 00:15:23.574
zenen gevorn geratevet.

00:15:23.833 --> 00:15:25.112
farshtendlekh

00:15:25.112 --> 00:15:29.442
gvirim hobn nisht oysgehaltn in Sibir. ven me shikt avek UNK mentshn

00:15:29.442 --> 00:15:31.342
vos zenen gevoynt tsu a poshet lebn

00:15:31.697 --> 00:15:34.290
iz epes andersh. m'hot avekgeshikt di gvirim.

00:15:34.566 --> 00:15:37.609
un dortn iz a sakh geshtorbn. a sakh zenen geblibn

00:15:37.609 --> 00:15:39.015
un a sakh geshtorbn.

00:15:42.615 --> 00:15:44.077
SO

00:15:44.134 --> 00:15:46.490
in di tsaytn, vos hot pasirt

00:15:46.716 --> 00:15:49.899
nokh di rusn zenen arayngekumen? vos hot, vos gedenkstu?

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:52.140
ikh gedenk az, zenen arayn

00:15:52.140 --> 00:15:54.660
hobn zey in eyn tog oysgekoyft ale gesheftn

00:15:54.660 --> 00:15:55.873
mit, mit di rublen.

00:15:56.335 --> 00:15:58.185
in eyn tog iz gornisht gevorn

00:15:59.338 --> 00:16:00.989
di gesheftn gevorn leydik.

00:16:00.989 --> 00:16:02.263
vos zey hobn gezen s-

00:16:02.263 --> 00:16:04.749
"vifl kost es? gib. vifl kost es? gib."

00:16:04.789 --> 00:16:07.479
un m'hot oysgekoyft ale gesheftn, tsvey tog UNK nisht geven

00:16:07.479 --> 00:16:09.259
nisht keyn esn un nisht keyn zakhn.

00:16:10.510 --> 00:16:11.468
in eyn tog.

00:16:11.468 --> 00:16:17.524
un nokh dem az s'hot zikh ongehoybn di g- di, di raye, m'iz geshtanen nokh tsuker, nokh broyt, nokh dem, nokh yenem

00:16:17.968 --> 00:16:20.442
in etlekhe teg hot zikh gebitn dos gantse lebn.

00:16:20.854 --> 00:16:22.535
un m'hot geshrign, "m'iz fray"

00:16:27.402 --> 00:16:30.503
un vayter shoyn gan dos lebn azoy, un di shules

00:16:30.503 --> 00:16:36.069
iz, bay undz iz geven, in di shule, hot men gelernt ⟨koym koym⟩ eyn

00:16:36.244 --> 00:16:40.186
hot men gelernt yidish UNK. ven zey zenen gekumen

00:16:40.260 --> 00:16:44.730
iz geven a lerer, Shtern, hot ongehoybn tsu zingen "lomir

00:16:44.730 --> 00:16:48.650
ale in eynem, in eynem," hot zikh ongehoybn tsu zingen shoyn lider

00:16:48.650 --> 00:16:51.360
fun, fun, fun farshidene zakhn. m'hot sh-

00:16:51.360 --> 00:16:54.990
m'iz, m'iz gevorn pyonern, mit royte bandlen.

00:16:54.990 --> 00:16:56.310
m'hot gedarft gebn

00:16:56.310 --> 00:16:58.640
dos vort az m'vet zayn getray

00:16:58.640 --> 00:17:01.570
far LENINen un far, f- far STALINen

00:17:01.570 --> 00:17:02.158
un s-

00:17:02.434 --> 00:17:05.814
s'iz gevorn gants ibergedreyt a naye lebn, un mir

00:17:05.814 --> 00:17:07.324
⟨personlekh⟩ hobn gemeynt

00:17:07.324 --> 00:17:09.820
az dos iz take a lebn. ale zenen glaykh

00:17:10.804 --> 00:17:13.593
ale ⟨vern⟩ normale shpeter. shpeter, nisht yetst

00:17:13.593 --> 00:17:14.999
s'iz gekumen a tsayt

00:17:15.141 --> 00:17:16.834
ale mentshn zenen farzorgt.

00:17:16.834 --> 00:17:19.095
yetst iz shver. shpeter vet vern laykhter.

00:17:19.095 --> 00:17:21.881
un dos lebn vet zikh hobn UNK shoyn, di yidn hobn take gemeynt

00:17:21.881 --> 00:17:23.501
az baym komunizm

00:17:23.501 --> 00:17:26.310
⟨veln zey⟩ zayn glaykh. UNK antisemitizm vet nisht zayn

00:17:26.310 --> 00:17:29.208
s'vet zayn yidishe shules. m'vet ales erloybn

00:17:30.750 --> 00:17:31.992
m'hot gegleybt

00:17:32.674 --> 00:17:36.836
vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn an- keyn, keyn andere idees iz nisht geven.

00:17:37.568 --> 00:17:40.346
nor mayn foter hot gezogt, er hot gezen

00:17:40.369 --> 00:17:43.552
az v- erger fun zey, fun di rusn, vet ⟨keyner⟩ nisht kumen.

00:17:43.761 --> 00:17:45.628
⟨az⟩ epes gegleybt in di daytshn.

00:17:45.668 --> 00:17:47.484
er hot gehandlt mit di daytshn.

00:17:47.592 --> 00:17:51.394
di daytshn v- er iz geven UNK. UNK bakante daytshn

00:17:51.394 --> 00:17:52.440
hot er gemeynt

00:17:52.440 --> 00:17:54.960
az dos gantse folk dos ⟨daytshs⟩ iz oykh mentshn.

00:17:55.455 --> 00:17:57.491
e- er iz nisht geven azoy fanatik

00:17:57.649 --> 00:18:00.900
vi, vi s- vi er hot gegleybt in dem.

00:18:02.340 --> 00:18:04.460
far dem UNK ⟨er⟩ iz geblibn.

00:18:07.909 --> 00:18:10.164
bistu geblibn in zelbn hoyz?

00:18:09.867 --> 00:18:11.379
in ⟨dem⟩ zelbn hoyz.

00:18:11.588 --> 00:18:13.860
ale tsuzamen, di gantse familye?

00:18:12.938 --> 00:18:14.479
di gantse familye

00:18:14.479 --> 00:18:16.442
un, un

00:18:16.532 --> 00:18:19.749
un s'iz geven, farshtendlekh, UNK shver tsu lebn.

00:18:21.915 --> 00:18:25.992
ikh veys vos d- denstmol epes, der foter hot gemakht epes ander arbet.

00:18:26.303 --> 00:18:31.275
ikh veys nisht vos er hot gemakht, vayl er fleg avekgeyn un kumen, mir ⟨hot er dertseylt⟩ vos er makht dortn vos

00:18:31.382 --> 00:18:33.704
nor er iz geven mit di noz arop.

00:18:34.605 --> 00:18:36.607
nisht, nisht der foter gevorn.

00:18:36.445 --> 00:18:38.953
d'host gezen az er hot zikh geendert.

00:18:37.305 --> 00:18:40.685
yo, kh'hob gezen az, az epes klapt nisht, nor

00:18:40.685 --> 00:18:43.003
kh'hob zikh ⟨nit⟩, nisht interesirt.

00:18:43.144 --> 00:18:45.197
vi alt bistu geven demoltst?

00:18:44.764 --> 00:18:48.639
n- dos iz geven nayn un draysik, elef yor. vos hob ikh gekent trakhtn dortn?

00:18:50.434 --> 00:18:52.717
er fleg avekgeyn in shul arayn gants fri

00:18:52.717 --> 00:18:54.554
un bay nakht, fleg kumen shpet.

00:18:54.554 --> 00:18:57.124
normal hob ikh im veynik gezen oykhet. er me-

00:18:57.124 --> 00:18:59.219
er fleg zayn mer in shul vi in shtub.

00:19:00.205 --> 00:19:04.353
friert bizn nayn un dray fleg er makhn ⟨lotereys⟩ in shul epes far

00:19:04.353 --> 00:19:05.432
far oreme

00:19:05.432 --> 00:19:09.980
l- shpiln v- zakhn geven in dortn, v- me fle-

00:19:09.980 --> 00:19:12.780
er fleg onfirn sotsyale zakhn fleg er onfirn

00:19:12.780 --> 00:19:16.432
vayl di mame fleg zogn "Srol Elye, kumst azoy shpet

00:19:16.624 --> 00:19:20.434
un farzorgstu d- undz, fargest fun undz."

00:19:20.434 --> 00:19:24.231
zogt er "s'iz, s'iz do a sakh imigrantn fun Poyln. me darf zey helfn."

00:19:24.231 --> 00:19:24.856
zo-

00:19:24.856 --> 00:19:29.021
zogt zi "hob in zinen dayn familye. s'iz ⟨genug⟩ mentshn do in di shtot

00:19:29.247 --> 00:19:32.931
vos zey kenen d- kenen oykh tun." zogt er "vart oys, Zisl

00:19:32.931 --> 00:19:35.518
du veyst nisht vos mit dayne kinder vet zayn."

00:19:37.313 --> 00:19:39.585
dos gedenkstu fun di tsaytn?

00:19:38.410 --> 00:19:39.264
⟨azoy iz dos⟩

00:19:39.709 --> 00:19:41.019
vayl s'iz geven bay nakht

00:19:44.164 --> 00:19:45.356
UNK

00:19:45.531 --> 00:19:47.055
iz er nisht geven keyn nar

00:19:47.055 --> 00:19:47.887
in dem.

00:19:49.918 --> 00:19:51.076
er hot gevust

00:19:51.336 --> 00:19:53.017
epes kokht zikh

00:19:56.466 --> 00:19:58.024
nor s'hot mir bagegnt

00:19:58.024 --> 00:19:59.272
ikh ken nisht fargesn

00:19:59.272 --> 00:20:00.040
a yid

00:20:00.040 --> 00:20:01.162
a alter yid.

00:20:01.162 --> 00:20:03.648
ven ikh fleg geyn in shule fleg ikh im zen

00:20:03.857 --> 00:20:07.074
a- ayngeboygn. er hot getrogn sforim

00:20:07.148 --> 00:20:09.336
farkoyfn varshayndlekh tsi vos

00:20:09.477 --> 00:20:12.941
un fleg "Simkhele, Simkhele, vos makhstu?" azoy o

00:20:12.941 --> 00:20:15.714
me fleg zikh freyen mit mir, far vos veys ikh nisht.

00:20:15.957 --> 00:20:18.313
un nokh dem in geto, ven mir zenen geven

00:20:18.403 --> 00:20:19.797
iz er tsugekumen

00:20:20.547 --> 00:20:25.209
e- zogt er mir "oy, mayn kind" zogt er. "me shekht undz. mir hobn gezindikt.

00:20:25.209 --> 00:20:26.429
me harget undz.

00:20:26.993 --> 00:20:29.453
"yemakh ⟨shemoy⟩" zogt er "az

00:20:29.453 --> 00:20:31.133
undz vet men bagrobn" zogt er

00:20:31.133 --> 00:20:33.543
"nor zey, vet men zayn ver zol bagrobn

00:20:33.543 --> 00:20:37.083
m'vet zey hargenen z- zikh hargenen eyner dem andern."

00:20:37.995 --> 00:20:39.254
dos iz zayne verter.

00:20:39.683 --> 00:20:41.314
"s'vet kumen a tsayt

00:20:41.337 --> 00:20:43.204
vos m'vet UNK batsoln far alemen.

00:20:43.345 --> 00:20:44.784
nisht mir" zogt er

00:20:44.784 --> 00:20:46.866
"zey veln zikh aleyn tsvishn zikh hargenen."

00:20:47.023 --> 00:20:48.463
un dos kumt yetst for.

00:20:48.463 --> 00:20:49.700
Yugoslavye

00:20:49.943 --> 00:20:51.897
kumt for tsvishn andere felker

00:20:51.897 --> 00:20:55.067
un dos geyt vos der mentsh hot gezogt fuftsik yor tsurik.

00:20:57.452 --> 00:20:59.895
dos vil zogn, s'iz geven mentshn kluge

00:20:59.895 --> 00:21:03.740
nor nisht oyf azoy klug, me zol vartn UNK hargenen tsvantsik toyznt mentshn.

00:21:04.017 --> 00:21:06.508
yeder hot gezogt "vi ken men azoy fil mentshn bagrobn?"

00:21:07.611 --> 00:21:10.963
s'iz geven a, a UNK dort, nor nisht aza groys.

00:21:12.285 --> 00:21:14.354
vos hot pasirt mit dayn shtot?

00:21:14.833 --> 00:21:18.320
mit undzer shtot, m'hot bombardirt

00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:20.480
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome

00:21:21.195 --> 00:21:22.805
hob i- hob ikh gezen

00:21:22.805 --> 00:21:25.105
azoy niderik di FLUGZEUGn daytshishe

00:21:25.105 --> 00:21:27.095
az ikh hob gezen dem kop funem f- pilot.

00:21:28.300 --> 00:21:34.116
un, un zey flegn tsu ersht bombardirn di kazarme, di shtot, umedum, u- un mir flegn aroysl-

00:21:35.185 --> 00:21:38.976
ikh f- epes, kh'veys nisht far vos. ikh fleg l- aroysloyfn kukn.

00:21:39.437 --> 00:21:40.916
d'host nisht moyre gehat?

00:21:39.488 --> 00:21:40.342
ho-

00:21:40.905 --> 00:21:44.409
ot dos iz di zakh, vayl ikh fleg mit di shkotsim zikh shlogn mit alemen

00:21:44.584 --> 00:21:47.109
hob ikh bakumen, on moyre geven.

00:21:47.183 --> 00:21:50.349
un ikh fleg nokh kukn a- az er flit durkh.

00:21:50.845 --> 00:21:53.421
ikh fleg imer dertseyln vifl kh'hob gezen eroplanen.

00:21:53.713 --> 00:21:55.643
nor vos zhe den? in di shtot

00:21:55.643 --> 00:21:57.823
vayter, mir zenen geven nokhn taykh.

00:21:57.823 --> 00:21:59.228
hot er zeyer bombardirt

00:21:59.228 --> 00:22:03.130
zeyer. ikh gedenk iz geven di rusishe

00:22:03.130 --> 00:22:05.280
pulemyotn firt tsuzamen mit vaser

00:22:05.280 --> 00:22:08.172
hob ikh gezen a vogn, shteyt un shist oyfn vogn

00:22:08.172 --> 00:22:09.442
un di vaser kokht.

00:22:09.442 --> 00:22:11.512
iz di koyln zenen nisht gan shoyn vayt

00:22:11.512 --> 00:22:13.102
zey ⟨zenen nisht ge- blaybn⟩ azoy.

00:22:15.330 --> 00:22:17.231
zey hobn gehat zeyer shvakh gever.

00:22:18.638 --> 00:22:19.647
s'iz

00:22:19.647 --> 00:22:21.956
s'iz in eyn tog a- ales aroys.

00:22:22.654 --> 00:22:27.761
kh'hob gezen di, di daytshn hobn zikh UNK tsunoyf. di ershte daytshn zenen nisht geven geferlekh, di ershte.

00:22:29.303 --> 00:22:31.372
vos, vos, di militer.

00:22:31.986 --> 00:22:34.927
di tsveyte zenen shoyn gekumen or- ordenung makhn.

00:22:34.927 --> 00:22:37.180
arayngekumen a daytsh mit, mit shikses

00:22:37.180 --> 00:22:41.041
m'hot oyfgemakht dem ⟨shlak⟩ m'hot aroysgenumen dem alem vos UNK geven, m'iz avek un fartik.

00:22:41.132 --> 00:22:41.986
eygene.

00:22:42.364 --> 00:22:44.805
dos hobn zey getun bay dir in shtub?

00:22:43.917 --> 00:22:46.982
yo, aroysgenumen vos zey hobn gevolt hobn zey aroysgen-

00:22:48.068 --> 00:22:50.947
mit di, mit di shiks- mit di polyatshkes, mit di ukrainer

