du bist geshtanen dos gez- dos gezen?

00:22:53.704 --> 00:22:55.419
ikh hob es gezen, yo.

00:22:56.033 --> 00:22:57.984
vos hostu getrakht in di tsaytn?

00:22:57.619 --> 00:23:01.393
vos hob ikh gekent trakhtn? ikh hob getrakht epes, kh'hob farshtanen.

00:23:01.602 --> 00:23:04.052
vos kent ir fartrakhtn yetst UNK ⟨kholilek⟩ UNK

00:23:04.052 --> 00:23:06.952
a erd ⟨treshenish⟩, kent ir trakhtn "dos iz a erd ⟨treshenish⟩."

00:23:07.322 --> 00:23:09.982
ver trakht denstmol? me farlirt dem seykhl oykhet.

00:23:12.722 --> 00:23:13.335
s'iz sh-

00:23:13.335 --> 00:23:15.061
dos iz shver yetst tsu zogn.

00:23:15.287 --> 00:23:16.967
ven mir voltn getrakht gut

00:23:16.967 --> 00:23:20.097
ven friert volt geven aza organizatsye vi yetst

00:23:20.248 --> 00:23:22.250
vos me nemt tsunoyf di mentshn

00:23:22.307 --> 00:23:23.822
un s'iz geven a onfirer

00:23:23.822 --> 00:23:26.570
voltn ale UNK ⟨getrakht⟩ s'iz nisht geven. m'iz geven tselozt.

00:23:27.184 --> 00:23:30.148
s'iz nisht geven keyn mentsh zol onfirn mit di mentshn.

00:23:31.015 --> 00:23:33.810
ikh veys ikh hob gepashet beheymes bay dem tshekh

00:23:33.816 --> 00:23:38.006
hob ikh di k- di ku gehaltn dortn, di ku dortn. s'iz geven ordenung bay mir

00:23:38.006 --> 00:23:39.416
ikh fleg zey traybn tsurik.

00:23:39.525 --> 00:23:42.956
un di, di k- di shefelekh vos mir zenen geven

00:23:43.452 --> 00:23:45.167
hot keyner nisht ongefirt.

00:23:45.291 --> 00:23:46.601
yeder hot getun

00:23:46.776 --> 00:23:48.047
vos er hot farshtanen.

00:23:48.047 --> 00:23:50.037
eyn mentsh v- vos iz geven

00:23:50.037 --> 00:23:52.407
onfirn, volt dos nisht pasirt azoy UNK.

00:23:52.407 --> 00:23:55.139
⟨m'volt⟩ antlofn in di velder. s'iz geven velder dortn.

00:23:55.483 --> 00:23:57.198
s'iz nisht geven vu tse loyfn oykhet

00:23:57.272 --> 00:23:58.869
vayl di goyim hobn geharget.

00:23:59.297 --> 00:24:00.188
s'iz geven a

00:24:00.188 --> 00:24:02.176
a, mamesh a

00:24:02.335 --> 00:24:05.732
me ken zikh afile nisht forshte- di generatsye ken dos nisht farshteyn

00:24:05.732 --> 00:24:07.678
az s'iz nisht geven vu tsu geyn.

00:24:08.190 --> 00:24:10.698
umedum hot, hot men gevart oyf dir.

00:24:11.076 --> 00:24:14.633
di bafelkerung iz geven shreklekh. di ukrainer zenen geven shreklekh.

00:24:14.633 --> 00:24:17.465
zey hobn ge- nokh geven erger fun di daytshn, di ukrainer.

00:24:18.872 --> 00:24:19.805
vi nokh?

00:24:19.716 --> 00:24:20.520
ha?

00:24:20.405 --> 00:24:22.205
v- vi nokh? in vos far a veg?

00:24:21.403 --> 00:24:25.906
v- z-, zey, zey flegn khapn yidn un oysgebn

00:24:25.906 --> 00:24:27.726
un aleyn hargenen oykhet.

00:24:27.663 --> 00:24:29.233
dos hostu gezen?

00:24:28.407 --> 00:24:32.884
dos hob ikh gezen. f- shpeter shoyn, nokh, nokh, ven UNK ⟨geven⟩ in di velder.

00:24:32.884 --> 00:24:33.660
s'iz geven

00:24:33.660 --> 00:24:35.560
s'iz geven b-

00:24:35.560 --> 00:24:40.010
BANDEROVTSES, s'iz geven BULBA BOROVETSES, s'iz geven MELNYKES. m'hot nisht gevust ver, ver vos

00:24:40.010 --> 00:24:41.620
tut, un nokh dem

00:24:41.620 --> 00:24:43.050
undz iz gevorn laykhter

00:24:43.050 --> 00:24:45.430
ven di ukrainer hobn ongehoybn hargenen polyakn.

00:24:45.838 --> 00:24:47.531
dos iz geven undzer mazl.

00:24:47.531 --> 00:24:50.355
vi azoy der yid UNK zikh hargenen eyner dem andern.

00:24:50.361 --> 00:24:52.650
der daytsh hot gegebn gever far di ukrainer

00:24:52.757 --> 00:24:55.586
un di polyakn hobn zikh gevo- di ukrainer hobn zikh gevolt

00:24:55.761 --> 00:24:59.771
opnemen nekome fun di polyakn, vayl zey hobn gezogt di polyakn hobn zey gedrukt.

00:24:59.845 --> 00:25:03.652
normal iz dos geven Rusland. di polyakn z- hobn es farkhapt.

00:25:03.878 --> 00:25:05.914
un zey zenen gevorn balebatim dortn.

00:25:06.207 --> 00:25:08.361
un ven di, un der daytsh

00:25:08.552 --> 00:25:11.516
hot ven, ven zey zenen arayngekumen

00:25:12.619 --> 00:25:16.831
hot, iz geven ongeshribn "HEIL HITLER, SLAVA UKRAINI."

00:25:16.956 --> 00:25:18.058
zol lebn

00:25:18.058 --> 00:25:19.042
Hitler

00:25:19.048 --> 00:25:22.535
un ba- un bafrayen Ukraine.

00:25:23.250 --> 00:25:26.462
hobn zey gekrogn shtolts, un di polyakn zenen gefaln, vayl

00:25:26.462 --> 00:25:27.238
vayl

00:25:27.238 --> 00:25:29.724
DEUTSCHLAND iz ongefaln o- oyf di poylishe.

00:25:29.865 --> 00:25:34.205
far dem vos zey zenen arayngekumen, gedenk ikh, hot nor gegebn broyt in di kleytn.

00:25:34.205 --> 00:25:36.545
iz geshtanen a raye goyim

00:25:36.683 --> 00:25:41.081
un a raye yidn. a yid hot nisht getort shteyn dortn. direkt toyt shtrof.

00:25:41.121 --> 00:25:43.750
iz fleg men araynlozn tsen goyim un eyn yid.

00:25:43.750 --> 00:25:46.886
shtelt zikh for vos far a yid hot gekent bakumen a shtikl broyt.

00:25:50.335 --> 00:25:51.493
un nokh dem

00:25:51.567 --> 00:25:55.864
di, ven di milkhome iz shoyn gegan, iz geven a sakh gefangene

00:25:56.106 --> 00:25:59.275
⟨bay mir iz a simkhe⟩, hob ikh gevolt zen vos se tut zikh dortn

00:25:59.275 --> 00:26:00.422
bay di kazarme.

00:26:00.422 --> 00:26:04.245
hot, fleg men, fleg men di, di, di gefangene

00:26:04.245 --> 00:26:05.836
a velt mit gefangene

00:26:06.062 --> 00:26:07.068
a velt.

00:26:07.328 --> 00:26:08.706
nisht, n-

00:26:09.083 --> 00:26:11.102
a sakh, toyznter mentshn.

00:26:11.209 --> 00:26:12.772
m'hot ⟨kholile⟩ UNK gegebn.

00:26:13.437 --> 00:26:16.570
iz, hot er sortirt, ukrainer bazunder

00:26:16.660 --> 00:26:18.990
rusn bazunder, un yidn bazunder.

00:26:18.990 --> 00:26:20.520
un komisarn bazunder.

00:26:20.777 --> 00:26:23.465
un ikh hob geshtanen bay, dort. ikh hob zikh tsugekukt.

00:26:23.465 --> 00:26:25.445
iz yidn hot men glaykh avekgefirt.

00:26:26.920 --> 00:26:29.270
un ver s'hot nisht oysgegebn zikh az er iz a yid

00:26:29.270 --> 00:26:30.980
hot im di ukrainer im oysgegebn.

00:26:30.980 --> 00:26:32.786
er hot zikh ⟨nisht⟩ gekent farshtekn dortn.

00:26:33.045 --> 00:26:35.519
UNK un yidn hot men glaykh tsugenumen.

00:26:35.830 --> 00:26:38.051
un nokh dem flegt men zey firn tsu di arbet

00:26:38.563 --> 00:26:42.213
un i- far vos fleg er geyn? ⟨der⟩ fleg geyn brengen holts fun di

00:26:42.213 --> 00:26:44.973
fun di tsebrokhene shtiber, fun di

00:26:44.973 --> 00:26:46.775
iz geven breter

00:26:47.018 --> 00:26:52.513
un ikh fleg geyn sh- shlepn breter, brengen aheym, ikh zol kenen kokhn.

00:26:52.890 --> 00:26:54.397
iz fleg ikh ales zen.

00:26:54.397 --> 00:26:58.819
iz fleg men avekshteln a, a mantl, di gefangene flegn arbetn

00:26:58.819 --> 00:27:02.244
un mentshn flegn varfn dos broyt, mel, kh'veys vos dortn.

00:27:02.244 --> 00:27:05.046
fleg tsugeyn a, a ukrainer tsi

00:27:05.046 --> 00:27:09.135
mitn ferd, un fleg avekshteln dos ferd, dos ferd fleg esn

00:27:12.735 --> 00:27:16.984
er fleg f- un nokh dem fun di arbet flegn zey geyn, fleg eyner shlepn dem andern

00:27:16.984 --> 00:27:20.204
un s'iz d- s'iz geven eynike vos zey hobn geshlept di fis afile.

00:27:20.515 --> 00:27:23.658
dos hot tsebrokhn di moral

00:27:23.658 --> 00:27:25.127
kegn di daytshn.

00:27:25.127 --> 00:27:27.934
dos, dos hot men ⟨propogandirt⟩

00:27:28.092 --> 00:27:29.233
f- oyfn front.

00:27:29.290 --> 00:27:32.222
m'hot gevizn varshayndlekh di ale tsores

00:27:32.222 --> 00:27:35.763
un shpeter hobn zikh shoyn soldatn veyniker untergegebn.

00:27:35.955 --> 00:27:39.054
denstmol hot zikh ongehoybn der kamf fun partizanen

00:27:39.263 --> 00:27:40.489
fun mentshn

00:27:41.187 --> 00:27:44.128
vos zey hobn gevust vos er tut mit di mentshn

00:27:44.128 --> 00:27:46.024
ven er harget nisht keyn yidn

00:27:47.768 --> 00:27:49.331
volt er nisht geven in Rusland

00:27:49.810 --> 00:27:51.401
ven er harget nisht keyn mentshn.

00:27:51.401 --> 00:27:53.347
s'iz a mazl vos er hot geharget

00:27:53.522 --> 00:27:55.426
vayl shpeter hot UNK ⟨dos⟩ tun

00:27:55.426 --> 00:27:57.111
er hot zikh gekent maskirirn

00:27:57.117 --> 00:27:59.547
er hot zikh gekent makhn vi a shefele

00:27:59.547 --> 00:28:02.037
aynnemen Rusland, un nokh dem derhargenen.

00:28:02.037 --> 00:28:04.080
a dank dem iz nokh geblibn mentshn.

00:28:05.149 --> 00:28:07.033
di partizanen hobn im

00:28:07.073 --> 00:28:08.501
a halb KAPUT gemakht.

00:28:09.469 --> 00:28:11.707
di goyim denstmol zenen shoyn geven mit di yidn.

00:28:13.468 --> 00:28:21.224
zog mir, vi nokh hobn di polyakn un di ukrainen gekent visn az du bist a yid in di tsaytn? vi, zey hobn dikh derkent? vi nor

00:28:20.168 --> 00:28:21.678
me- a yidishe shule.

00:28:21.678 --> 00:28:24.278
ikh hob gehat shvartse hor un gedreyte hor

00:28:24.278 --> 00:28:26.288
un m'iz geven a, a ekhter yid.

00:28:26.327 --> 00:28:29.021
fun di vaytns, fun a kilometer hot men mir derkent derkenen

00:28:29.263 --> 00:28:34.454
nokh eyn zakh, di shule, di kinder, eyner mitn tsveytn kind, s'iz geven eyn shule do un eyn shule do.

00:28:35.018 --> 00:28:36.514
dos iz geven mayn mazl.

00:28:37.330 --> 00:28:39.216
ven ikh bin a, ⟨gevoynt⟩ kind

00:28:39.216 --> 00:28:40.698
a ⟨farpestet⟩ kind

00:28:40.806 --> 00:28:43.483
fun a yidishe shule, volt ikh nisht ibergelebt.

00:28:44.198 --> 00:28:46.504
UNK tsugegreyt tsum kamf.

00:28:49.868 --> 00:28:51.347
ikh bin shoyn geven a soldat.

00:28:51.893 --> 00:28:53.953
di kinder yetst vos ikh kuk dikh tsu

00:28:53.953 --> 00:28:56.033
der ken nisht shvimen, der ken nisht shlogn

00:28:56.162 --> 00:28:58.513
de- de- der hot moyre far epes andersh

00:28:58.513 --> 00:28:59.753
un de- i- der

00:28:59.753 --> 00:29:02.363
der vil zikh ontun azoy vi, vi andere

00:29:02.380 --> 00:29:03.670
er vil nokh zayn a porets

00:29:03.670 --> 00:29:04.920
er vil zayn farzorgt

00:29:05.190 --> 00:29:07.431
mir makhn di kinder mit dem shlekht.

00:29:07.431 --> 00:29:09.050
a kind darf kenen shvimen.

00:29:09.050 --> 00:29:11.840
a kind ⟨darf kenen⟩ forn. a kind darf visn tsores

00:29:11.928 --> 00:29:14.718
a kind darf ales visn. layder, s'iz nisht gut

00:29:15.079 --> 00:29:16.575
nor ⟨se⟩ muz zayn.

00:29:17.695 --> 00:29:21.590
a kind vos vakst oys ⟨oyf greytn⟩ mit alemen, dos iz nisht keyn kind.

00:29:24.681 --> 00:29:26.770
halt a minut, m'vet makhn
